Name: Box Runner!
About the game: 'Box Runner! ' is a 2D platform jumping game, the game is simple to operate, the atmosphere is relaxed, and the cartoon picture is suitable for casual play for a while. 【Game Operation】 The player presses the space bar to jump, and presses the space bar twice to perform a double jump. 【Game Features】 Players need to collect more gold coins to get high scores. Players can use double jumps to navigate complex terrain.
